  <title>Office Hours</title>

  <p>Office hours are times that I have scheduled to meet with and talk to you outside of class time. I have a physical office in <em>MHAB 121</em> and a <xref ref="zoom">Virtual Zoom Office</xref>. You may schedule an appointment to reserve a specific time if desired, but you are <em>always welcome</em> to stop by without one during my regular office hours:
<ul>
    <li>
        <p>
            Monday-Thursday: 1:00 pm to 2:00 pm
    <ul>
        <li>
            <p>
                Both in-person and virtual for Weeks 1-4.
            </p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p>
                Virtual only for Weeks 3-6.
            </p>
        </li>
    </ul>
        </p>
    </li>
</ul></p>
<p>I'm here to help! Because my schedule can fluctuate a bit week-to-week due to meetings, be sure to check the <alert>Meet with Mrs. Green</alert> link in the Canvas navigation menu for my most up-to-date availability. From there, you can either plan a time to drop in or lock in a reserved appointment spot. If the times listed don't fit your schedule, just send me a Canvas message and we will find a time that works.</p>
